{"tid":597783,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全國人民代表大會不如改返個名","createTime":"2018-03-19T03:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T03:54:32.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e60ef83269c2b0d9b138bfa0add155323b71b64c","tid":597783,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"叫全國政要代表大會好過啦。<br />\n<br />\n修憲、國家主席取消連任限期，國家主席連任。<br />\n<br />\n咁大爭議性的政治議題，都可以99％通過。好明顯不能代表人民，也不代表人民的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n直接叫做「全國政要代表大會」， 或者 「全國高官代表大會」更加名符其實啦。"},{"pid":"a9d97b3625ef76759a987069cf9920ee362fc474","tid":597783,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"不記名投票，都可以99％通過<br />\n<br />\n證明呢班代表，真係代表了高官，不代表人民。"},{"pid":"53f8e2df17a7f119b7a62de9e786d527a8f85824","tid":597783,"uid":163684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"但我認為全中國市民投票<br />\n結果都係一樣"},{"pid":"dc0170ccca4a14fe084cc2309ba9300d02c36f5d","tid":597783,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f8e2df17a7f119b7a62de9e786d527a8f85824","tid":597783,"uid":163684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"但我認為全中國市民投票<br />\n結果都係一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"起碼唔會99％支持咁痴線先啦<br />\n可能係6成至7成支持，3成至4成反對"},{"pid":"32c9cb6ced395b397509fde553114dc169e68c64","tid":597783,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"最醒係你"},{"pid":"4caff766fc249fb4c822623e2fd09013fc511b1f","tid":597783,"uid":7237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗支那啲人已經慣咗人大唔係代表全國人民好耐"},{"pid":"ef7e45b5ab8300f99e93f9a286438d343caa2bc3","tid":597783,"uid":7237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d97b3625ef76759a987069cf9920ee362fc474","tid":597783,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB